I will using the Buiness model or MercadoLibre, Inc. buinees model as they are the major contributors to e-commerce industry in Emerging Markets of South America. 
MercadoLibre is a technology-driven company that is focused on the local market in Latin America. It offers a variety of products and services, including e-commerce, payments, lending, and insurance. The company is profitable and has been growing rapidly in recent years.

MercadoLibre's business model can be applied to an emerging markets project by:

Localizing the products and services to meet the needs of the local market.
Using technology to solve problems and improve the customer experience.
Diversifying the business to reduce risk.
Being profitable to ensure sustainability.
Growing the business by expanding into new markets, launching new products and services, or acquiring other businesses.

